('Mike Lemon Consulting SL', 'Accountancy/Tax', 'English-speaking accountancy and taxation firm serving UK expats in Marbella and the Costa del Sol for over 50 years. Specializing in Spanish tax for UK expats with fully bilingual English-Spanish services. Core tax services include Income Tax Return Modelo 100, Wealth Tax Return Modelo 714, Non-Residential Tax Return Modelo 210, and Overseas Assets Form 720 reporting. Additional services include holiday lettings registration, conveyancing, Spanish wills preparation, UK taxation and accounts, insurance brokerage, Spanish lessons, and house maintenance coordination. Registered HMRC agents for UK tax filing requirements. Friendly, personal service helping hundreds of families enjoy life in Spain without financial and legal worries. Experienced in dealing with Hacienda (Spanish tax authority) and providing transparent communication with digital document submission.', 'Urb. El Faro, 285 Calle Córdoba', 'Marbella', 'Málaga', '+34 952 199 007', 'lemonsinspain@gmail.com', 'https://www.lemon.consulting/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
